0.4
    - FEATURE: added `cdn` management commands
    - FEATURE: added `-x` option to `put`
    - FEATURE: added `tmplink` command
0.3
    - BUGFIX: Better handling of SSL errors during auth
    - BUGFIX: Fix issue when displaying endpoint defaults
0.2
    - FEATURE: added `endpoint default` command
    - FEATURE: `get` now takes a `-d` option to download files into a
          particular directory
    - FEATURE: `get` now takes a `-a` option to download all files in
          container
    - FEATURE: `ls` now handles pseudo-hierarchical folders (CloudFiles)
0.1
    - Initial release
